  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nWhy should this feature exist?\r\n`For situations where an unexpected shut down of the blockchain occurs `\r\nWhat are the use-cases?\r\n`Resolving the following error`\r\n```\r\nINFO [05-10|22:41:55.756] Opened ancient database                  database=/run/media/dirtybits/Elements/geth/chaindata/ancient readonly=false\r\nFatal: Failed to register the Ethereum service: failed to retrieve genesis from ancient EOF\r\n\r\n```\r\n# Implementation\r\nDo you have ideas regarding the implementation of this feature?\r\n```\r\nfinding the last COMPLETE db entry or allowing the user to specify which hash, block, or entry they would like to start over at.`\r\nMonero, TurtleCoin have similar features.\r\n```\r\nAre you willing to implement this feature?\r\n`Possibly in the future`",
