    "body": "Yeah, so the `*.0000` files are all empty:\r\n\r\n```\r\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 dirtybits dirtybits          0 May 10 18:40 bodies.0000.cdat\r\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 dirtybits dirtybits          0 May 10 18:40 diffs.0000.rdat\r\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 dirtybits dirtybits          0 May 10 18:40 hashes.0000.rdat\r\n-rwxrwxrwx 1 dirtybits dirtybits          0 May 10 18:40 headers.0000.cdat\r\n```\r\n\r\nInterestingly the receipts.0000 is not empty.\r\n\r\nCould you upload the `*.cidx` files somewhere for us? Seems something nuked out the first data files from each dataset. \r\n\r\nCan you share what environment you're running in? Perhaps there was some permission issue in some virtualization, or an OS crash?",
